name: Registrar
label: registrar
definition: party that has the capacity to act as a representative of a registration authority to provide registration services, including official record keeping

name: Registry
label: registry
explanatoryNote: Electronic registries typically contain a unique identifier for each entry, so that individual records can be referenced from other documents and registries.
definition: authoritative record or collection of records relating to something

name: RegistrationAuthority
definition: service provider that is responsible for maintaining a registry and provides registration services
label: registration authority

name: RegistryIdentifier
definition: identifier associated with an entry in a registry, i.e., one that provides an index into the registry for the identified item
label: registry identifier

name: RegistryEntry
label: registry entry
definition: independently identified entry for something recorded in a registry

name: RegistrationCapacity
label: registration capacity
definition: the capacity of some natural person to formally register information in a registry on behalf of some registration authority

name: RegistrationScheme
definition: scheme for organizing information and allocating identifiers to items in a registry
label: registration scheme

name: RegistrationService
label: registration service
definition: service provided to individuals and/or organizations to register items in a registry

name: registers
definition: records something in a registry or archive
label: registers

name: hasRegistrationDate
label: has registration date
definition: the date or date and time on which something is recorded

name: isRegisteredBy
definition: indicates the registration authority or registrar that registers something
label: is registered by

name: hasRegistryEntry
definition: links a registry to entries that it contains
label: has registry entry

name: isRegistrationAuthorityFor
label: is registration authority for
definition: indicates the thing (typically an identifier or code) that the registration authority has authority for

name: isRegisteredIn
label: is registered in
definition: indicates the registry that something is registered in

name: hasRegistrationAuthority
label: has registration authority
definition: indicates the registration authority for something
